  "title": "3D Modeller",
  "description": "<ul><li>Responsible for all preparation drawings, coordination of drawings, technical drawings/detailing, and documentations</li><li>Making presentations with BIM related software as required by the project team</li><li>Carry out modelling and shop drawings as instructed and finish in a timely manner</li><li>Support project team with design engineering works</li><li>Ensure all drawings are incompliant with project specifications & requirements.</li><li>Clarify and raise RFI for any discrepancies. Coordinate/communicate with internal and external teams members & consultants.</li><li>Use of BIM/CAD to do Shop drawings / Construction drawings / As Build drawings documentations.</li><li>Check subcontractor system drawings CAD/Models and submissions prior to coordination.</li><li>Liaise with internal project members, subcontractors, clients and consultants to issue Coordinated drawings for approval/construction</li><li>Ensure that clashes highlighted are resolved or concluded, if not continuous monitoring for resolutions to be provided by the project team.</li><li>Perform and maintain proper documentation of clash detection reports.</li><li>Manage the process of coordination, Exchange of data, and collaboration of BIM with project stakeholders</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <a href=\"mailto:davidnhbsg@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com; </strong></a><strong>ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
